{"product_id":"madara-magnetic-blush-mineral-cheek-blusher-2-bare-blossom-6g-copy","title":"MÁDARA Magnetic Blush Mineral Cheek Blusher, #2 Cold Cheeks, 6g","description":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eFrom vibrant red beet juice to subtle high-tech powder formulas, blush has remained a timeless classic throughout the decades and trends. This satin matte blush blends seamlessly with your complexion for a natural, skin-like flush that barely looks made up. The talc-free formula features glycolipid-coated mineral pigments that adapt to your skin's unique texture, delivering a flawlessly smooth finish for the most natural-looking blush.  \u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use: \u003c\/strong\u003eDiffuse a small amount on the cheeks, nose and eyelids for a naturally flushed look. Layer on the cheeks for a lifted appearance. \u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e MICA (CI 77019)**; CALCIUM CARBONATE; KAOLIN; LAUROYL LYSINE; ORYZA SATIVA (RICE) STARCH; RAPHANUS SATIVUS (RADISH) ROOT EXTRACT; ZINC STEARATE; SILICA; CAPRYLIC\/CAPRIC TRIGLYCERIDE; ARGANIA SPINOSA (ARGAN) KERNEL OIL*; CAPRYLYL GLYCOL; CELLULOSE; TOCOPHEROL; MALTODEXTRIN; GLYCINE SOJA (SOYBEAN) OIL*; MAGNESIUM STEARATE; CITRIC ACID; AQUA; GLYCERIN; GLYCOLIPIDS; POLYGLYCERYL-3 DIISOSTEARATE; ORYZA SATIVA (RICE) EXTRACT; ORYZA SATIVA (RICE) GERM EXTRACT; ASCORBYL PALMITATE; AROMA; LINALOOL***; GERANIOL***; GERANYL ACETATE***; VANILLIN; CI 77491 (IRON OXIDES)**\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e*Ingredients from organic farming\u003cbr\u003e**Pure mineral pigments\u003cbr\u003e***From natural essential oils\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e100% Natural origin of total\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"productPage-ingredientMessage-3FP\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"richContent-root-3Sy\"\u003ePlease note that ingredient lists may change and slightly vary from time to time. You will always find the most up-to-date information on the actual product packaging.\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"richContent-root-3Sy\"\u003e\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCOSMOS NATURAL certified\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c!----\u003e","brand":"MADARA","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":52636519956807,"sku":null,"price":24.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/madara-magnetic-blush-mineral-cheek-blusher-2-cold-cheeks-6g-5364256.jpg?v=1762389133","url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/products\/madara-magnetic-blush-mineral-cheek-blusher-2-bare-blossom-6g-copy","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}